sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant Storage as BlobStorageService
    participant Domain as UserLibraryEntry
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events
    participant DocProc as DocumentProcessing

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/library/games/{gameId}/pdf
    Note right of Client: Multipart form with PDF file

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract file from form
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create UploadCustomGamePdfCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(command)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Check file size ≤ 50 MB
    Validator->>Validator: Verify MIME type = application/pdf
    Validator->>DB: Verify user owns game in library
    DB-->>Validator: Entry found ✓
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Get library entry
    DB-->>Handler: UserLibraryEntry

    Handler->>Storage: UploadAsync(file, path)
    Storage->>Storage: Generate S3 key
    Storage->>Storage: Upload to blob storage
    Storage-->>Handler: Upload successful (documentId)

    Handler->>Domain: entry.AssociatePrivatePdf(documentId)
    Domain->>Domain: Set PrivatePdfDocumentId
    Domain->>Events: Raise PrivatePdfUploadedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(entry)
    DB-->>Handler: Entry updated ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish PrivatePdfUploadedEvent
    Events->>DocProc: Trigger extraction pipeline

    Handler-->>Mediator: UserLibraryEntryDto
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: UserLibraryEntryDto

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {entryId, privatePdfDocumentId}

    Note over DocProc: Background processing starts
    DocProc->>DocProc: Extract text (3-stage pipeline)
    DocProc->>DocProc: Create chunks
    DocProc->>DocProc: Index in Qdrant
    DocProc->>Events: Publish PdfIndexedEvent
